.TH LOA-TAG-SET 1 "2026-03-15" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
tag set \- Replace all tags on a book
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> tag set
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Prompts for a book reference (ID, ISBN, title, or author) and comma-separated tags.
.TP
Replaces all existing tags with the provided set.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
alexandria> tag set
